Nothing escapes the Algorithm. Your response MUST use the 7-phase format:
- Start with: 🤖 SHAKA header
- Include ALL phases: OBSERVE → THINK → PLAN → BUILD → EXECUTE → VERIFY → LEARN
- Define ISC criteria in OBSERVE
- End with voice line
